This program creates a popup in which you can enter several pieces of information, after which it gives popups with
the information you entered.

create screen
    add text box for name
    add text box for age
    add text box for height in cm
    add text box for weight in kg
    add button to submit

when submit button is pressed
    create popup with "Hello <name>!"
    create popup with "You are <age> years old!"
    create popup with "You are <height> cm tall!"
    create popup with "You weigh <weight> kg!"